{"tid":1407602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔割］今時今日仲批評磚/鐵/隧 一定係三毛/鬼","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T13:50:45.000Z","uid":132892,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8e983d1286989425ccacaac51519bcb1b6b045","tid":1407602,"uid":132892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"近三罷呢两日又好多割席Post帶風向<br />\n主要針對衝/不合作運動<br />\n批評佢地冇唔合理/冇用/反效果<br />\n<br />\n佢地其實冇錯 暴力係唔啱 阻街係唔啱 破壞係唔啱<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n示威者對死物發泄遠不及警黑合作暴力<br />\n示威者佔路遠不及政府阻礙社會發展<br />\n示威者破壞遠不及官商鄉警黑對法治破壞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有意見 請先去聲討make action 嘅罪魁 唔係去質問被make reaction嘅迫害者</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不要說：示威者我覺得唔係好好</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">試著說：官商警鄉黑我屌你老母</span><br />\n<br />\n有時間就討論三罷 再帶風向話割就負評/Block/上一頁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2dc3218d22b74d7664a3f3b48a49af77a0ad206","tid":1407602,"uid":132892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:46:02.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279691f9745e9cb348d150df2bfe0302c0c6543e","tid":1407602,"uid":132892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"三毛偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3ddbf91abe78fcc75a4b24e9a79083081d1db1","tid":1407602,"uid":132892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:50:45.000Z","msg":"今日又一大堆割post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}